Assignment 5
Question
● Create a gitflow workflow architecture on git
● Create all the required branches
● Starting from the feature branch, push the branch to the master, following the
architecture
● Push a urgent.txt on master using hotfix

Answer
Commands Used
1.  mkdir gitflow-project  
2.  cd gitflow-project  
3.  git init  
4.  git branch develop  
5.  git branch release  
6.  git branch hotfix  
7.  git checkout develop  
8.  git branch feature1  
9.  git branch feature2  
10. git checkout feature1  
11. touch feature1.txt  
12. git add feature1.txt  
13. git commit -m "Add feature1.txt in feature1 branch"  
14. git checkout develop  
15. git merge feature1  
16. git checkout release  
17. git merge develop  
18. git checkout master  
19. git merge release  
20. git branch hotfix-urgent  
21. git checkout hotfix-urgent  
22. touch urgent.txt  
23. git add urgent.txt  
24. git commit -m "Add urgent.txt via hotfix"  
25. git checkout master  
26. git merge hotfix-urgent  




